    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or bolstering fatigue, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule. For the buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
